ENGLISH Mr President , I am speaking on behalf of the Group of the Party of European Socialists in support of Mr Pronk 's words on behalf of the Committee as a whole . 
ENGLISH I have to say that I was not totally satisfied by the Commissioners' responses , in that the documents that were referred to , with which we are familiar , as Mr Pronk said , need to contain time frames and rather more practical decision . 
